               <scopecontent id="aspace_04590f4937726c218b724752c666ab56">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>The Corpuscle was the "Official Organ of tghe Alumni Association of Rush Medical College, Chicago, Ill." The article, "James Henry Etheridge, A.M., M.D.: In Memoriam" (volume 8, pp. 273-276 and portrait) was presented to the faculty by Prof. James B. Herrick.</p>
